    <body>
      <lg type="poem" rend="case(upper)">
        <l>Mooses come walking <pb/>up over the hill</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>Mooses come walking <pb/>they rarely stand still.</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>When Mooses come walking <pb/>they walk where they will</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>and mooses come walking <pb/>up over the hill.</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>Mooses look into <pb/>your window at night,</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>They look to the left <pb/>and they look to the right.</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>The mooses are smiling <pb/>they think it’s a zoo</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>And that’s why the mooses <pb/>like looking at you.</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>So, if you see mooses <pb/>while lying in bed</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>It’s best just to lay there <pb/>pretending you’re dead.</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>The mooses will leave <pb/>and you’ll get the thrill</l>
        <pb/>
        <l>Of seeing the mooses <pb/>go over the hill.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
